                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base"><strong>Medicare Plus</strong> was engineered to bridge this gap. By building a unified, multi-role portal system that integrates CRM and CMS workflows, we remove physical friction. Our program enables rapid, direct settlements, immediate clinical verifications, and complete employee transparent audits.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-100">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i></div>
                        <div><h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Instant Authorization</h4><p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Real-time claim updates</p></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-medBlue-50 text-medBlue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-lock"></i></div>
                        <div><h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Protected Credentialing</h4><p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Role-restricted entry</p></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex justify-center">
                <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full -z-10 animate-pulse"></div>
                <div class="expert-img-clip w-full max-w-md h-[460px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative border-4 border-white bg-slate-200">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Collaborative corporate strategy">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-medBlue-900/80 to-transparent p-8 flex flex-col justify-end text-white">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Designed for Organizations</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">Reducing manual claim times from days to a few simple click validations across all business departments.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- INTERACTIVE CALCULATOR SECTION -->
<div class="py-20 bg-slate-100 border-t border-b border-slate-200" id="calculator">
