            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-medBlue-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Savings Simulator</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-medBlue-900 mt-2">See What Your Business Saves</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Estimate the hours and processing fees you save by converting from spreadsheets to our digital Medicare Plus architecture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-200/60 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">
                        <span>Number of Corporate Employees</span>
                        <span class="text-medBlue-600" id="emp-slider-val">250 Employees</span>
                    </div>
                    <input type="range" id="emp-slider" min="10" max="2500" value="250" class="w-full h-2 bg-slate-200 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer accent-medBlue-600" oninput="calculateSavings()">
                </div>
